#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an10.87"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.87:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.87:0.2"
msgid "9. Theravagga "
msgstr "9. Senior Mendicants "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 87. Nappiyasutta → adhikaraṇikasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an10.87:0.3"
msgid "87. Nappiyasutta "
msgstr "87. Disciplinary Issues "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
#. VAR: kālaṅkataṃ bhikkhuṃ → kalandakaṃ bhikkhuṃ (bj) | kāḷakabhikkhuṃ (s1-3) | kālakaṃ bhikkhuṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "an10.87:1.1"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā kālaṅkataṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants concerning the mendicant Kalandaka: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.87:1.2"
msgid "“bhikkhavo”ti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.87:1.3"
msgid "“Bhadante”ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. "
msgstr "“Venerable sir,” they replied. "

msgctxt "an10.87:1.4"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "The Buddha said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an10.87:2.1"
msgid "“Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu adhikaraṇiko hoti, adhikaraṇasamathassa na vaṇṇavādī. "
msgstr "“Firstly, a mendicant raises disciplinary issues and doesn’t praise the settlement of disciplinary issues. "

msgctxt "an10.87:2.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu adhikaraṇiko hoti adhikaraṇasamathassa na vaṇṇavādī, ayampi dhammo na piyatāya na garutāya na bhāvanāya na sāmaññāya na ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. (1) "
msgstr "This quality doesn’t conduce to warmth, respect, esteem, harmony, and unity. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.165, sc3
#. VAR: sikkhāsamādānassa → sikkhākāmassa (mr)
msgctxt "an10.87:3.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na sikkhākāmo hoti, sikkhāsamādānassa na vaṇṇavādī. "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant doesn’t want to train, and doesn’t praise taking up the training. … "

msgctxt "an10.87:3.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na sikkhākāmo hoti sikkhāsamādānassa na vaṇṇavādī, ayampi dhammo na piyatāya na garutāya na bhāvanāya na sāmaññāya na ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. (2) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an10.87:4.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu pāpiccho hoti, icchāvinayassa na vaṇṇavādī. "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant has bad desires, and doesn’t praise getting rid of desires. … "

msgctxt "an10.87:4.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu pāpiccho hoti icchāvinayassa na vaṇṇavādī, ayampi dhammo na piyatāya na garutāya na bhāvanāya na sāmaññāya na ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. (3) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an10.87:5.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kodhano hoti, kodhavinayassa na vaṇṇavādī. "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant is irritable, and doesn’t praise getting rid of anger. … "

msgctxt "an10.87:5.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kodhano hoti kodhavinayassa na vaṇṇavādī, ayampi dhammo na piyatāya na garutāya na bhāvanāya na sāmaññāya na ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. (4) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an10.87:6.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu makkhī hoti, makkhavinayassa na vaṇṇavādī. "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant denigrates others, and doesn’t praise getting rid of denigration. … "

msgctxt "an10.87:6.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu makkhī hoti makkhavinayassa na vaṇṇavādī, ayampi dhammo na piyatāya na garutāya na bhāvanāya na sāmaññāya na ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. (5) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an10.87:7.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu saṭho hoti, sāṭheyyavinayassa na vaṇṇavādī. "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant is devious, and doesn’t praise getting rid of deviousness. … "

msgctxt "an10.87:7.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu saṭho hoti sāṭheyyavinayassa na vaṇṇavādī, ayampi dhammo na piyatāya na garutāya na bhāvanāya na sāmaññāya na ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. (6) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an10.87:8.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu māyāvī hoti, māyāvinayassa na vaṇṇavādī. "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant is deceitful, and doesn’t praise getting rid of deceitfulness. … "

msgctxt "an10.87:8.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu māyāvī hoti māyāvinayassa na vaṇṇavādī, ayampi dhammo na piyatāya na garutāya na bhāvanāya na sāmaññāya na ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. (7) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.166, sc9
msgctxt "an10.87:9.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu dhammānaṃ na nisāmakajātiko hoti, dhammanisantiyā na vaṇṇavādī. "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant doesn’t pay attention to the teachings, and doesn’t praise attending to the teachings. … "

msgctxt "an10.87:9.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu dhammānaṃ na nisāmakajātiko hoti dhammanisantiyā na vaṇṇavādī, ayampi dhammo na piyatāya na garutāya na bhāvanāya na sāmaññāya na ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. (8) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "an10.87:10.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na paṭisallīno hoti, paṭisallānassa na vaṇṇavādī. "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant is not in retreat, and doesn’t praise retreat. … "

msgctxt "an10.87:10.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na paṭisallīno hoti paṭisallānassa na vaṇṇavādī, ayampi dhammo na piyatāya na garutāya na bhāvanāya na sāmaññāya na ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. (9) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
#. VAR: paṭisanthārako → paṭisandhārako (mr)
msgctxt "an10.87:11.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sabrahmacārīnaṃ na paṭisanthārako hoti, paṭisanthārakassa na vaṇṇavādī. "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant is inhospitable to their spiritual companions, and doesn’t praise hospitality. "

msgctxt "an10.87:11.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sabrahmacārīnaṃ na paṭisanthārako hoti paṭisanthārakassa na vaṇṇavādī, ayampi dhammo na piyatāya na garutāya na bhāvanāya na sāmaññāya na ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. (10) "
msgstr "This quality doesn’t conduce to warmth, respect, esteem, harmony, and unity. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc12
msgctxt "an10.87:12.1"
msgid "Evarūpassa, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno kiñcāpi evaṃ icchā uppajjeyya: "
msgstr "Even though a mendicant such as this might wish: "

#. VAR: garuṃ kareyyuṃ → garukareyyuṃ (bj, s1-3, pts1)
#. VAR: garuṃ karonti → garukaronti (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an10.87:12.2"
msgid "‘aho vata maṃ sabrahmacārī sakkareyyuṃ garuṃ kareyyuṃ māneyyuṃ pūjeyyun’ti, atha kho naṃ sabrahmacārī na ceva sakkaronti na garuṃ karonti na mānenti na pūjenti. "
msgstr "‘If only my spiritual companions would honor, respect, esteem, and venerate me!’ Still they don’t honor, respect, esteem, and venerate them. "

msgctxt "an10.87:12.3"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "an10.87:12.4"
msgid "Tathāhissa, bhikkhave, viññū sabrahmacārī te pāpake akusale dhamme appahīne samanupassanti. "
msgstr "Because their sensible spiritual companions see that they haven’t given up those bad unskillful qualities. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.167, sc13
msgctxt "an10.87:13.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, assakhaḷuṅkassa kiñcāpi evaṃ icchā uppajjeyya: "
msgstr "Suppose a wild colt was to wish: "

msgctxt "an10.87:13.2"
msgid "‘aho vata maṃ manussā ājānīyaṭṭhāne ṭhapeyyuṃ, ājānīyabhojanañca bhojeyyuṃ, ājānīyaparimajjanañca parimajjeyyun’ti, atha kho naṃ manussā na ceva ājānīyaṭṭhāne ṭhapenti na ca ājānīyabhojanaṃ bhojenti na ca ājānīyaparimajjanaṃ parimajjanti. "
msgstr "‘If only the humans would put me in a thoroughbred’s place, feed me a thoroughbred’s food, and give me a thoroughbred’s grooming.’ Still the humans wouldn’t put them in a thoroughbred’s place, feed them a thoroughbred’s food, or give them a thoroughbred’s grooming. "

msgctxt "an10.87:13.3"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "an10.87:13.4"
msgid "Tathāhissa, bhikkhave, viññū manussā tāni sāṭheyyāni kūṭeyyāni jimheyyāni vaṅkeyyāni appahīnāni samanupassanti. "
msgstr "Because sensible humans see that they haven’t given up their tricks, bluffs, ruses, and feints. "

msgctxt "an10.87:13.5"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, evarūpassa bhikkhuno kiñcāpi evaṃ icchā uppajjeyya: "
msgstr "In the same way, even though a mendicant such as this might wish: "

msgctxt "an10.87:13.6"
msgid "‘aho vata maṃ sabrahmacārī sakkareyyuṃ garuṃ kareyyuṃ māneyyuṃ pūjeyyun’ti, atha kho naṃ sabrahmacārī na ceva sakkaronti na garuṃ karonti na mānenti na pūjenti. "
msgstr "‘If only my spiritual companions would honor, respect, esteem, and venerate me!’ Still they don’t honor, respect, esteem, and venerate them. "

msgctxt "an10.87:13.7"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "an10.87:13.8"
msgid "Tathāhissa, bhikkhave, viññū sabrahmacārī te pāpake akusale dhamme appahīne samanupassanti. "
msgstr "Because their sensible spiritual companions see that they haven’t given up those bad unskillful qualities. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc14
msgctxt "an10.87:14.1"
msgid "Idha pana, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na adhikaraṇiko hoti, adhikaraṇasamathassa vaṇṇavādī. "
msgstr "Next, a mendicant doesn’t raise disciplinary issues and praises the settlement of disciplinary issues. "

msgctxt "an10.87:14.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na adhikaraṇiko hoti adhikaraṇasamathassa vaṇṇavādī, ayampi dhammo piyatāya garutāya bhāvanāya sāmaññāya ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. (1) "
msgstr "This quality conduces to warmth, respect, esteem, harmony, and unity. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc15
msgctxt "an10.87:15.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sikkhākāmo hoti, sikkhāsamādānassa vaṇṇavādī. "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant wants to train, and praises taking up the training. … "

msgctxt "an10.87:15.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sikkhākāmo hoti sikkhāsamādānassa vaṇṇavādī, ayampi dhammo piyatāya garutāya bhāvanāya sāmaññāya ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. (2) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc16
msgctxt "an10.87:16.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu appiccho hoti, icchāvinayassa vaṇṇavādī. "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant has few desires, and praises getting rid of desires. … "

msgctxt "an10.87:16.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu appiccho hoti icchāvinayassa vaṇṇavādī, ayampi dhammo … pe … ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. (3) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc17
msgctxt "an10.87:17.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu akkodhano hoti, kodhavinayassa vaṇṇavādī. "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant is not irritable, and praises getting rid of anger. … "

msgctxt "an10.87:17.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu akkodhano hoti kodhavinayassa vaṇṇavādī, ayampi dhammo … pe … ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. (4) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc18
msgctxt "an10.87:18.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu amakkhī hoti, makkhavinayassa vaṇṇavādī. "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant doesn’t denigrate others, and praises getting rid of denigration. … "

msgctxt "an10.87:18.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu amakkhī hoti makkhavinayassa vaṇṇavādī, ayampi dhammo … pe … ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. (5) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.168, sc19
msgctxt "an10.87:19.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu asaṭho hoti, sāṭheyyavinayassa vaṇṇavādī. "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant isn’t devious, and praises getting rid of deviousness. … "

msgctxt "an10.87:19.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu asaṭho hoti sāṭheyyavinayassa vaṇṇavādī, ayampi dhammo … pe … ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. (6) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc20
msgctxt "an10.87:20.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu amāyāvī hoti, māyāvinayassa vaṇṇavādī. "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant isn’t deceitful, and praises getting rid of deceitfulness. … "

msgctxt "an10.87:20.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu amāyāvī hoti māyāvinayassa vaṇṇavādī, ayampi dhammo … pe … ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. (7) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc21
msgctxt "an10.87:21.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu dhammānaṃ nisāmakajātiko hoti, dhammanisantiyā vaṇṇavādī. "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant pays attention to the teachings, and praises attending to the teachings. … "

msgctxt "an10.87:21.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu dhammānaṃ nisāmakajātiko hoti dhammanisantiyā vaṇṇavādī, ayampi dhammo … pe … ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. (8) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc22
msgctxt "an10.87:22.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu paṭisallīno hoti, paṭisallānassa vaṇṇavādī. "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant is in retreat, and praises retreat. … "

msgctxt "an10.87:22.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu paṭisallīno hoti paṭisallānassa vaṇṇavādī, ayampi dhammo … pe … ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. (9) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc23
msgctxt "an10.87:23.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sabrahmacārīnaṃ paṭisanthārako hoti, paṭisanthārakassa vaṇṇavādī. "
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant is hospitable to their spiritual companions, and praises hospitality. "

msgctxt "an10.87:23.2"
msgid "Yampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sabrahmacārīnaṃ paṭisanthārako hoti paṭisanthārakassa vaṇṇavādī, ayampi dhammo piyatāya garutāya bhāvanāya sāmaññāya ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. (10) "
msgstr "This quality conduces to warmth, respect, esteem, harmony, and unity. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc24
msgctxt "an10.87:24.1"
msgid "Evarūpassa, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno kiñcāpi na evaṃ icchā uppajjeyya: "
msgstr "Even though a mendicant such as this might never wish: "

msgctxt "an10.87:24.2"
msgid "‘aho vata maṃ sabrahmacārī sakkareyyuṃ garuṃ kareyyuṃ māneyyuṃ pūjeyyun’ti, atha kho naṃ sabrahmacārī sakkaronti garuṃ karonti mānenti pūjenti. "
msgstr "‘If only my spiritual companions would honor, respect, esteem, and venerate me!’ Still they honor, respect, esteem, and venerate them. "

msgctxt "an10.87:24.3"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "an10.87:24.4"
msgid "Tathāhissa, bhikkhave, viññū sabrahmacārī te pāpake akusale dhamme pahīne samanupassanti. "
msgstr "Because their sensible spiritual companions see that they’ve given up those bad unskillful qualities. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.169, sc25
msgctxt "an10.87:25.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, bhaddassa assājānīyassa kiñcāpi na evaṃ icchā uppajjeyya: "
msgstr "Suppose a fine thoroughbred never wished: "

msgctxt "an10.87:25.2"
msgid "‘aho vata maṃ manussā ājānīyaṭṭhāne ṭhapeyyuṃ, ājānīyabhojanañca bhojeyyuṃ, ājānīyaparimajjanañca parimajjeyyun’ti, atha kho naṃ manussā ājānīyaṭṭhāne ca ṭhapenti ājānīyabhojanañca bhojenti ājānīyaparimajjanañca parimajjanti. "
msgstr "‘If only the humans would put me in a thoroughbred’s place, feed me a thoroughbred’s food, and give me a thoroughbred’s grooming.’ Still the humans would put them in a thoroughbred’s place, feed them a thoroughbred’s food, and give them a thoroughbred’s grooming. "

msgctxt "an10.87:25.3"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "an10.87:25.4"
msgid "Tathāhissa, bhikkhave, viññū manussā tāni sāṭheyyāni kūṭeyyāni jimheyyāni vaṅkeyyāni pahīnāni samanupassanti. "
msgstr "Because sensible humans see that they’ve given up their tricks, bluffs, ruses, and feints. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc26
msgctxt "an10.87:26.1"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, evarūpassa bhikkhuno kiñcāpi na evaṃ icchā uppajjeyya: "
msgstr "In the same way, even though a mendicant such as this might never wish: "

msgctxt "an10.87:26.2"
msgid "‘aho vata maṃ sabrahmacārī sakkareyyuṃ garuṃ kareyyuṃ māneyyuṃ pūjeyyun’ti, atha kho naṃ sabrahmacārī sakkaronti garuṃ karonti mānenti pūjenti. "
msgstr "‘If only my spiritual companions would honor, respect, esteem, and venerate me!’ Still they honor, respect, esteem, and venerate them. "

msgctxt "an10.87:26.3"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "an10.87:26.4"
msgid "Tathāhissa, bhikkhave, viññū sabrahmacārī te pāpake akusale dhamme pahīne samanupassantī”ti. "
msgstr "Because their sensible spiritual companions see that they’ve given up those bad unskillful qualities.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.87:26.5"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

